#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/color_smudge_engine.rst:362
msgid ""
"Up to 1.00 each for brushes with less density or non fully-opaque predefined "
"brushes"
msgstr ""
"密度の低いブラシ、あるいは完全不透明ではない定義済みブラシの場合は、最大は"
